  "content": "## Config\n## Server Integration\n\n### New REST endpoints\n\n```\nPOST /v1/context    — context-only mode (R+A)\nPOST /v1/ask        — full RAG mode (R+A+G)\n```\n\nRequest body (shared):\n```json\n{\n  \"query\": \"How does authentication work?\",\n  \"scope_id\": \"project-alpha\",\n  \"limit\": 10,\n  \"expand_graph\": true\n}\n```\n\n\n### New MCP tools\n\n```\ncorvia_context   — context-only (returns assembled context + sources)\ncorvia_ask       — full RAG (returns generated answer + sources + trace)\n```\n",
